Chords
======
A chord generator lib for guitar-like instruments.


Running irb under chords/lib:

>> require 'chords/fretboard'
=> true
>> include Chords
=> Object
>> Fretboard.standard.print E.major, :duplicates => 3, :max_fret_distance => 2

E: --0----0----0----0---12----0---12--
B: --9----0----0---12---12---12---12--
G: --9----9----1---13---13---13---13--
D: --9----9----2---14---14---14---14--
A: -11---11----2---14---14---14---14--
E: --0----0----0----0----0---12---12--

Total 7 fingerings.
=> nil
>>
